, of course be correct. This also applies to Gaston's French and that of the other French people in the book. I hope there are no slips there. Elsewhere there are bits of deliberately faulty French.





Sincerely yours,

Vladimir Nabokov





TO: MAURICE GIRODIAS

CC, 6 pp.





Goldwin Smith Hall

Cornell University

Ithaca, N.Y.

July 9, 1955

